name: Primitive Star Ornament
description: Beautiful primitive star ornament, very versatile and can be used not only for the holiday season but also for everyday decor. Hand hooked with 100% wool strips with a burlap backing and ready to be hung. Other colors and sizes available for ordering!

name: Stocking & Mitten Christmas Ornaments
description: These two ornaments will be a great addition to any Chistmas tree this coming season. Both are hand hooked by myself personally in 100% wool strips with a burlap backing and ready to be hung. Additional quantities and colors can be ordered per your request, just allow additional time as these are not created till payment is received.

name: Primitive Star Coaster
description: This beautiful 6x6 1/4 hand hooked coaster could be a wonderful additon in any home.  This piece is very versatile and could be used in a number of ways such as a wall hanging, framed, with your favorite mug of coffee!  This piece was hooked personally by myself in #8 wool stripes.  It is accented in the center with a brick red primitive star with fall colors surrounding it with a slate colored border and binded off with black yarn.

name: Dark Circles
description: This one of a kind mat has a modern twist.  This piece is done in darker tones in 100% wool, with a burlap backing and a black yarn edge binding.  It could be used as a wall hanging, a center piece on a table, or framed.  The size is 8 1/4x5 1/2 and can also be made in additional sizes and colors.

name: Fall Foliage
description:
Beautiful cherry framed 12 x 16 piece hand hooked personally by myself. This one of a kind piece has an array of fall rustic tones such as oranges, yellows, and browns. There is a burlap backing and the whole piece is hooked in 100% wool strips. This piece can be hung on your wall, set on a fireplace mantel, or on a shelf. Sure to be a beautiful attention spotlight in any home!

This piece can also be custom ordered in different color tones, patterns, or sizes at no addtional cost.
